element.name: Where Is Black Rock? by toczygroszek, Unknown Cache (5/2.5)

description.p: This is a really difficult puzzle cache placed in Blackrock and all is in black-rock theme. Coordinates are for reference only. At the beginning you have to solve the puzzle below:

long-description.p:
You will probably visit this area more than once. It will take you loads of thinking and searching. Maybe a better name for this cache would be "Blackrock Nightmare"
The cache was a small tupperware container with three nice black rocks for the 1st three finders, but now is micro and contain logbook only, so please BYOP.
Important: Logs without an actual note in the logbook will be deleted!
Good luck!!!
